description:
Stuck with Hackett - Leaving on a Jet Train

Original Air Date: Aug 18, 2011
Runtime: 21 minutes
Video: AVC
Audio: AAC

Hackett pieces together a personal locomotive from pieces and parts found in an abandoned rail yard requiring him to use ingenuity and skill as he motorizes a Victorian-era handcart with a hydrogen flame and turns wood into an explosive gas.
